CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FPlans to build a new five-story hotel
OL,7,Fnear Jersey Airport have been given
OL,8,Fthe green light, after the island's
OL,9,FPlanning Committee unanimously
OL,10,Fapproved the development in principle
OL,11,Fat a meeting this morning (Wednesday
OL,12,F19 March).
OL,14,FThe Strive Hotel will be built next to
OL,15,Fthe existing Strive Health Club in St
OL,16,FPeter.
OL,18,FProposals include 155 rooms, a
OL,19,Fconference centre, a restaurant and
OL,20,Fcafe, three bars, a swimming pool, and
OL,21,Fa spa.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FBen Harvey, the CEO of Strive, says he
OL,7,Fis "delighted" with the decision and
OL,8,Fis looking forward to "building
OL,9,Fsomething that the island can be proud
OL,10,Fof".
OL,12,FThe decision comes after the original
OL,13,Fplans were rejected last November on
OL,14,Fthe grounds that the development was
OL,15,Ftoo large, "overly dominant", and
OL,16,Frisked damaging the landscape.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FThe plans also contravened Jersey's
OL,7,FBridging Island Plan (BIP) - the
OL,8,Fframework the government uses to
OL,9,Fbalance the need for new building
OL,10,Fprojects and infrastructure
OL,11,Fdevelopments with the need to protect
OL,12,Fnatural resources and the environment.
OL,14,FIt was concluded that the original 179-
OL,15,Fbed, six-storey building was not
OL,16,Fsufficiently "appropriate to the
OL,17,Ftownscape character of the area", as
OL,18,Fit would be the largest development
OL,19,Foutside of St Helier and in a
OL,20,Fdesignated green zone area.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FThe revised plans made changes that:
OL,8,FThese changes encouraged the island's
OL,9,FPlanning Committee to reverse its
OL,10,Fdecision.
OL,12,FHowever, the new plans do still
OL,13,Fcontravene the BIP.
OL,15,FPlanning Officer Sarah Jones says
OL,16,Fwhilst the proposed site of
OL,17,Fdevelopment is technically a green
OL,18,Fzone, it "is not considered as
OL,19,Fsensitive to change as other part of
OL,20,Fthe countryside, reflective of its
OL,21,Flocation opposite the built up area."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FShe adds a strong case was made for
OL,7,Fthe economic benefits building this
OL,8,Fkind of high-end luxury hotel could
OL,9,Fbring to Jersey.
OL,11,F"The development will expand on the
OL,12,Frange of visitor accommodation
OL,13,Favailable on the island", she explains.
OL,15,F"Based on the advice of colleagues in
OL,16,Fthe Department of Economy, it would
OL,17,Fhave a 'significant strategic impact'
OL,18,Fon the visitor economy".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FPaul Murphy, CEO of Jersey Business,
OL,7,Fdescribes the approval as "incredibly
OL,8,Fpositive".
OL,10,F"It's been a challenge to think about
OL,11,Fhow we develop a hotel in this
OL,12,Fparticular part of the island, and I
OL,13,Fthink the outcome is a very positive
OL,14,Fthing for our island economy and
OL,15,Fparticularly the visitor economy", he
OL,16,Fexplains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,F"When you look at the island-wide
OL,7,Feconomic benefit - which many parties
OL,8,Fhave, including Jersey Business - all
OL,9,Fparties are in absolute agreement
OL,10,Fthat, whatever level you take this at,
OL,11,Fit will drive benefits."
OL,13,FBen Harvey further explains that
OL,14,FStrive have developed their plans with
OL,15,Fthe hope of attracting a specific pool
OL,16,Fof visitors to the island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,F"We're trying to attract a big hotel
OL,7,Fchain here - and they bring an
OL,8,Fenormous marketing opportunity for the
OL,9,Fisland, to bring new people here
OL,10,Fwho've not been here before", he
OL,11,Fexplains.
OL,13,FThe hotel is also hoping to attract
OL,14,Fhigh-level sports teams.
OL,16,F"We've had a lot of approaches from
OL,17,Fthe Premier League having seen the
OL,18,FLions (rugby team) come over.
OL,26,@zD@GpmzD@Rpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,F"Sport is important to this island,
OL,7,Fand therefore bringing the best people
OL,8,Ffrom all over the world to come and
OL,9,Fvisit here gives children a huge boost
OL,10,F- they can see their heroes - and
OL,11,Fthat's exactly what we want to try and
OL,12,Fdo here.
OL,14,F"Those clubs demand that they have
OL,15,Faccommodation right next to their
OL,16,Ftraining facilities - so this isn't
OL,17,Fsomething we've just plucked out of
OL,18,Fthe air."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FHowever, concerns remain that the
OL,7,Fdecision to contravene the BIP in this
OL,8,Finstance risks setting a dangerous
OL,9,Fprecedent.
OL,11,FAlastair Layzell, the island's former
OL,12,FPlanning Chair, believes the
OL,13,Fdevelopment will ruin "an area of the
OL,14,Fcountryside we have said we will
OL,15,Fprotect".
OL,17,F"This is going to be a Goliath in the
OL,18,Fgreen zone, a colossal in the
OL,19,Fcountryside", he explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,F"It's all the more remarkable because
OL,7,F16 weeks ago the Planning Department
OL,8,Fsaid that it was totally contrary to
OL,9,Fpolicy.
OL,11,F"In between then and now there's been
OL,12,Finserted into the department an
OL,13,Feconomics team who were dismayed by
OL,14,Fthe decision (in November) and today
OL,15,Fyou see the result.
OL,17,F"It's a result this Committee will
OL,18,Fhave to live with - it is their legacy
OL,19,Fto the island."
OL,26,@vD@NpmvD@Zpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774048278
OL,3,CFive-story hotel development in green
OL,4,Czone given the green light
OL,6,FHowever, the plans have only been
OL,7,Fapproved in principle.
OL,9,FStrive will now have to work alongside
OL,10,Fthe Planning Department to put forward
OL,11,Fa fully comprehensive planning
OL,12,Fapplication that details exactly what
OL,13,Fthe building will look like and what
OL,14,Fits function will be.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/12
